    <newsTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Multiplayer Experiences Are Expanding]]></Value>
    </newsTitle>
    <newsExcerpt>
      <Value><![CDATA[We're bringing the Moo crew together for new multiplayer races, soccer matches, and tag adventures.]]></Value>
    </newsExcerpt>
    <newsBody>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>New multiplayer modes are landing in MooSoccer, MooRash, and MooTag — letting friends team up across the world.</p><p>Stay tuned for cross-platform play, new arenas, and weekly tournaments.</p>]]></Value>
